ring deep link generation that reflectively initializes\nevery lazy collection of the entity. On objects with very large\ncollections (e.g. a user role with 240k members) this loads and\nL2-caches every member entity, taking 30+ seconds of CPU per request.\n\nOnly *, :all and :simple actually expand to the transient href property,\nso only those (and a literal href field) now trigger link generation.\nResponse payloads are unchanged for all field values.\n\nAI Assisted","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"netroms@gmail.com"},"id":"7dd3fdbfae50e00a21eb3580af5500dfd868300b","tree_id":"20bb14a0166bc3d65f14bb29fc86d0092506636d","timestamp":"2026-07-19T12:26:15Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"netroms@gmail.com"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"},"name":"dhis2-core","full_name":"dhis2/dhis2-core","description":"DHIS 2 Core. Written in Java. Contains the service layer and Web API.","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core","fork":false,